title: EU Commission Boss Issues Another Coronavirus Apology as Bloc Cracks
description: European Commission President Ursula von der Leyen has issued another apology to Italy over the European Union's lack of solidarity during the Wuhan coronavirus outbreak.
content:
European Commission President Ursula von der Leyen has issued another apology to Italy over the European Union’s lack of solidarity during the Chinese coronavirus outbreak.
